  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the trial is to examine the effect of budesonide treatment on collagenous colitis.
      All patients is treated for 6 weeks with budesonide and thereafter randomised to 24 weeks
      treatment with placebo or continued budesonide. The end poit is effect on clinical symptoms
      (number of daily stools)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
